# Metric Resource: SequenceMatchRatio
<https://w3id.org/soel/metric/SequenceMatchRatio> a dqv:Metric ;

    dcterms:identifier "https://w3id.org/soel/metric/SequenceMatchRatio" ;
    dcterms:title "Token-level string similarity comparison"@en ;
    rdfs:label "SequenceMatchRatio: Token-level string similarity comparison"^^xsd:string ;
    vivo:abbreviation "sequence_match"^^xsd:string ;
    dcat:version "0.0.1"^^xsd:string ;
    ftr:status "Active"@en ;
    dcat:landingPage <https://w3id.org/soel/metric/SequenceMatchRatio> ;

    # Descriptive Content
    dcterms:description """
This metric aims to evaluate the token-level similarity between the generated label and the gold standard ontology.

**Calculation Process:**

1. Find the longest contiguous match between the generated label and any label in the gold standard ontology.

2. After the best match is found, extend the match while symbols keep matching.

3. Recurse on the left and right regions around that match to get more matching blocks;

4. Let M is the total matched elements across all matching blocks, the final result is 2*M / (len(generated_label) + len(gold_standard_label))

5. The range of SequenceMatchRatio is between 0 and 1. Higher ratio indicate better match.

**Example:** 

Generated_label: wine region

Gold_standard_label: region of wine

Result: 

Match_1: region

Match_2: wine

SequenceMatchRatio(Generated_label, Gold_standard_label) = 2*(12/25) = 0.48

**What is being measured?**

This metric captures partially matching or reordered expressions.
""" ;
    dcat:keyword "Ontology Concept Matching"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Metric"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Classes"@en ;
    
    # Relationships and Provenance
    dpv:isApplicableFor <https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q184754> ;
    ftr:hasBenchmark <https://w3id.org/soel/benchmark/ALL> ;
    <http://semanticscience.org/resource/SIO_000234> <https://w3id.org/soel/test/SequenceMatchRatio> ; # Has Implementation
    ftr:supportedBy <https://w3id.org/soel/> ;
    dqv:inDimension  "Ontology Engineering"^^xsd:string ;
    
    # Provenance
    dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
